title: of Montreal - A Pollinaire Rave - 7 tracks EP + 14 tracks EP
description:
These are two very rare EPs by of Montreal. Please keep in mind that even though both are called A Pollinaire Rave, they are completely different and both are well worth listening to.

The first one, containing 7 tracks, has circulated around online but is very hard to track down.

The other, with 14 tracks, is even harder to find and I don't believe it's currently, at the time of this upload, even on any private tracker or website.

Please read the included txt file for some more information.
		

--discopig
